collectors <- data2018 %>% 
  distinct(Collectors) %>% 
  pull()
Collector <- map_chr(collectors, \(current_collectors){
  knit_child(
    input = "field_child_doc.qmd",
    envir = env(),
    quiet = TRUE
    )
})

cat(Collector, sep = "\n")

## Sample Table

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
  #gt() %>%
  #tab_style(style = cell_fill(color = "lightgreen"),
  #          locations = cells_body(columns = c(CollMethod, SampleDepth),
  #                                 rows = CollMethod == "CO-E" & SampleDepth == 4)) %>%
  # cols_align(align = "center")
sample_table
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>%
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

## Controls Summary

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
  #gt() %>%
  #tab_style(style = cell_fill(color = "lightgreen"),
  #          locations = cells_body(columns = c(CollMethod, SampleDepth),

  # cols_align(align = "center")
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

## Controls Summary

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
  #gt() %>%
  #tab_style(style = cell_fill(color = "lightgreen"),

  # cols_align(align = "center")
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

## Controls Summary

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
  #gt() %>%
  #tab_style(style = cell_fill(color = "lightgreen"),
  #          locations = cells_body(columns = c(CollMethod, SampleDepth),
  #                                 rows = CollMethod == "CO-E" & SampleDepth == 4)) %>%
  # cols_align(align = "center")
sample_table
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>%
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

## Filter Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Filter Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
filter_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(FilterName) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
filter_table
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

::: panel-tabset
## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

## Filter Table

```{.r .cell-code}
filter_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(FilterName) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
filter_table
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
filter_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(FilterName) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(SiteVisitID, WaterBody, SiteCode, SiteVisitStartTime, SiteDepth) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center") %>%
  tab_header(title = "Site information")
```

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Weather, SamplingAirTemp, RivCond, WaterLevel, FoamRank, FoamSource, SiteVisitComment) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center") %>%
  tab_header(title = "Abiotic Factors")
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
filter_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
```

## Collection Information

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Weather, SamplingAirTemp, RivCond, WaterLevel, FoamRank, FoamSource, SiteVisitComment) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center") %>%
  tab_header(title = "Abiotic Factors")
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Sample Table

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
  #gt() %>%
  #tab_style(style = cell_fill(color = "lightgreen"),
  #          locations = cells_body(columns = c(CollMethod, SampleDepth),
  #                                 rows = CollMethod == "CO-E" & SampleDepth == 4)) %>%
  # cols_align(align = "center")
sample_table
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Collection Information

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Weather, SamplingAirTemp, RivCond, WaterLevel, FoamRank, FoamSource, SiteVisitComment) %>%
  distinct() %>%
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

### Collector 13 : JMP;  SJWK

## Sample Table

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
  #gt() %>%
  #tab_style(style = cell_fill(color = "lightgreen"),
  #          locations = cells_body(columns = c(CollMethod, SampleDepth),
  #                                 rows = CollMethod == "CO-E" & SampleDepth == 4)) %>%
  # cols_align(align = "center")
sample_table
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Weather, SamplingAirTemp, RivCond, WaterLevel, FoamRank, FoamSource, SiteVisitComment) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center") %>%
  tab_header(title = "Abiotic Factors")
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Sample Table

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
  #gt() %>%
  #tab_style(style = cell_fill(color = "lightgreen"),
  #          locations = cells_body(columns = c(CollMethod, SampleDepth),
  #                                 rows = CollMethod == "CO-E" & SampleDepth == 4)) %>%
  # cols_align(align = "center")
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
```

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Weather, SamplingAirTemp, RivCond, WaterLevel, FoamRank, FoamSource, SiteVisitComment) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center") %>%
  tab_header(title = "Abiotic Factors")
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
  #gt() %>%
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
pH_secchi_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Weather, SamplingAirTemp, RivCond, WaterLevel, FoamRank, FoamSource, SiteVisitComment) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center") %>%
  tab_header(title = "Abiotic Factors")
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
pH_secchi_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Filter Table

```{.r .cell-code}
filter_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(FilterName) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
```

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
```

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Weather, SamplingAirTemp, RivCond, WaterLevel, FoamRank, FoamSource, SiteVisitComment) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center") %>%
  tab_header(title = "Abiotic Factors")
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

## Filter Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Filter Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
filter_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(FilterName) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
filter_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Weather, SamplingAirTemp, RivCond, WaterLevel, FoamRank, FoamSource, SiteVisitComment) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center") %>%
  tab_header(title = "Abiotic Factors")
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

## Filter Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Filter Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
filter_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(FilterName) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
filter_table
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

::: panel-tabset
## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Weather, SamplingAirTemp, RivCond, WaterLevel, FoamRank, FoamSource, SiteVisitComment) %>%
  distinct() %>%
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

```{.r .cell-code}
filter_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(FilterName) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

::: panel-tabset
## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
```{=html}
<div id="ejyhpuzxhp" style="padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;overflow-x:auto;overflow-y:auto;width:auto;height:auto;">
<style>#ejyhpuzxhp table {
  font-family: system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji';
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

::: panel-tabset
## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(SiteVisitID, WaterBody, SiteCode, SiteVisitStartTime, SiteDepth) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center") %>%
  tab_header(title = "Site information")
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

## Controls Summary

A section at the beginning or at the end of each file summary report for a run sampled on a specific day could also summarize all the flags detected.

::: panel-tabset
## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  distinct() %>%
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

## Controls Summary

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

```{.r .cell-code}
  select(SiteVisitID, WaterBody, SiteCode, SiteVisitStartTime, SiteDepth) %>%
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```

### Collector 24 : TJM;JMP;JRP;

## Sample Table

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sample_table <- data2018 %>% 
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>% 
  select(SampleName, ProjectCode, CntrType, QCType, CollMethod, SampleDepth, LabAbbrev) %>% 
  group_by(LabAbbrev) %>% 
  distinct() #%>% #removes all the row that are the same, unsure if we are keeping them
  #gt() %>%
  #tab_style(style = cell_fill(color = "lightgreen"),
```

## Result Table

::: {.cell tbl-cap='Results Table'}

```{.r .cell-code}
result_table <- data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(ProfileDepth, Const, Result, QCType) %>%
  filter(!(Const %in% c("Secchi", "pH"))) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result,
              values_fn = list(Result = list)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(ProfileDepth)) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_align(align = "center")
result_table
```

## Controls Summary

## Collection Information

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  mutate(PrimCollector = str_extract(Collectors, "^[A-Za-z]{2,3}")) %>%
  select(RunCode, RunDate, PrimCollector) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  gt()
```

## DO and Temperature

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data2018$SampleDatetime <- as.POSIXct(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%m/%d/%Y %H:%M:%S")

data2018$Date <- as.Date(data2018$SampleDatetime)
data2018$Time <- format(data2018$SampleDatetime, format = "%H:%M:%S")

data2018 %>%
  filter(Collectors == "current_collectors") %>%
  select(Const, Result, QCType, Date, Time ) %>%
  filter(Const %in% c("Secchi","pH")) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = c(Const, QCType),
              values_from = Result) %>%
  gt()
```
